    <!-- Problem Section -->
    <section id="problem" class="problem">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>The Crisis in Bundibugyo</h2>
            </div>
            
            <div class="problem-content">
                <div class="problem-text">
                    <h3>Mountains of the Moon in Peril</h3>
                    <p>The Rwenzori Mountains, known as the "Mountains of the Moon," are facing an unprecedented environmental crisis that threatens the very existence of this unique ecosystem and the communities that depend on it.</p>
                    
                    <h4>Key Threats:</h4>
                    <ul style="margin: 20px 0 20px 30px;">
                        <li><strong>Glacial Retreat:</strong> Over 60% of glaciers have disappeared since 1900, with complete loss projected by 2030</li>
                        <li><strong>Landslides & Floods:</strong> Steep slopes and intense rainfall cause devastating landslides like the 2020 disaster that killed 100+ people</li>
                        <li><strong>Deforestation:</strong> 30% forest cover loss since 1990 due to charcoal production and farmland expansion</li>
                        <li><strong>Biodiversity Loss:</strong> Habitat destruction threatens endemic species like the Rwenzori duiker and chimpanzees</li>
                        <li><strong>Agricultural Collapse:</strong> Coffee and cocoa crops failing due to erratic rainfall and soil erosion</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <p>"When the glaciers vanish, our rivers will die. Our children ask why the snow is disappearing – what do we tell them?" <br><em>- Farmer in Bundibugyo</em></p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="problem-image">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506535995048-638aa1b62b77?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Rwenzori Mountain Crisis">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Solutions Section -->
    <section id="solutions" class="solutions">
