            </div>
            
            <div class="solution-cards">
                <div class="solution-card">
                    <div class="solution-image">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1448375240586-882707db888b?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Reforestation">
                    </div>
                    <div class="solution-content">
                        <h3>Reforestation Initiative</h3>
                        <p>Planting native trees to stabilize slopes, absorb CO₂, and restore critical habitats for endangered species.</p>
                        <div class="cost">$5,000 for 10,000 trees</div>
                        <p><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: var(--secondary); margin-right: 5px;"></i> Impact: Restores watersheds, creates wildlife corridors</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="solution-card">
                    <div class="solution-image">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1587049633312-d628ae50a8ae?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Beehive Fences">
                    </div>
                    <div class="solution-content">
                        <h3>Beehive Fences</h3>
                        <p>Installing beehive barriers to protect farms from elephants while creating sustainable honey income.</p>
                        <div class="cost">$3,500 for 50 fences</div>
                        <p><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: var(--secondary); margin-right: 5px;"></i> Impact: Reduces human-wildlife conflict, creates new livelihoods</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="solution-card">
                    <div class="solution-image">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542601906990-b4d3fb778b09?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Early Warning System">
                    </div>
                    <div class="solution-content">
                        <h3>Landslide Early Warning System</h3>
                        <p>Installing rain gauges and community alert systems to provide life-saving warnings before disasters strike.</p>
                        <div class="cost">$8,000 protects 5 villages</div>
                        <p><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: var(--secondary); margin-right: 5px;"></i> Impact: Saves lives, protects homes and farmland</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

