                        </div>
                        <h3>Robert Kato</h3>
                        <p>Community Coordinator</p>
                        <p>Born and raised in Bundibugyo, coordinates with local communities</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <div class="team-photo">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Sarah Johnson">
                        </div>
                        <h3>Sarah Johnson</h3>
                        <p>International Partnerships</p>
